<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.6.4">
<l>oṉṟē yuraippā ṉorucollē colluvaṉ</l>
<l>tuṉṟu muṭiyāṉ turiyō taṉaṉpakkal</l>
<l>ceṉṟaṅkup pāratam kaiyeṟin tāṉukku</l>
<l>kaṉṟukaḷ mēyppatōr kōlkoṇṭuvā</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṭalniṟa vaṇṇaṟkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bring one staff for grazing calves [to] him</l>
<l rend="indent">who says only one thing and says just one word,</l>
<l rend="indent">who took a vow [to join] the Bhārata war</l>
<l rend="indent">and went there to Duryodhana with a thick crown.</l>
<l>Bring a staff to the one with a complexion the colour of the sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
